devdoc.author: Your Name
devdoc.details: A smart contract for creating and managing decentralized polls

params._options: Array of voting options (2-6 options allowed)

finishPoll(uint256).details: Finish a poll (only creator can call this)

params._pollId: The ID of the poll to finish

getAllPollOptions(uint256).details: Get all options for a poll

returns.voteCounts: Array of vote counts for each option

returns.voteCount: Number of votes for this option

getTotalPolls().details: Get the total number of polls created

getUserPolls(address).details: Get polls created by a specific user

returns._0: Array of poll IDs created by the user

getVoterChoice(uint256,address).details: Get the choice made by a voter

returns._0: The option index chosen by the voter

hasUserVoted(uint256,address).details: Check if an address has voted on a specific poll

vote(uint256,uint256).details: Vote on a specific poll option

params._optionIndex: The index of the chosen option

devdoc.title: Pollify - Decentralized Polling System
